quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juu…óe Mun On mawnii, ko Kanko woni hattan…óo kala huunde"
  67,2,"On tagir…óo maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude golle. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, Haforoowo On"
  67,3,On tagu…óo kammuuli jee…ói…ói fawondir…ói. A yi'ataa …ďura-…ďurda e tagu Jom hinaraŇčke On. Yiltu ndaar…óe maa …óen (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ceekol
  67,4,"Refti ruttaa ndaar…óe …óen laa…ďi …ói…ói, gite maa …óen ruttoto e maa…óa hara ko …óe hoy…óe, ta∆īii…óe"
  67,5,"Gom…óii Men cu…óinirii kammu aduna ngun [koode] pitilli, Men wa…ói …óe fi…óir…óe seytanuuji, Men hebilani …ďe lette Hu…ď…ďunge negn"
  67,6,"Hino woodani …ďen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  67,7,"Si …ďe weddaama e nder magge, …ďe naniray nge haacaango, hara hinge fata"
  67,8,"Hinge e…ď…ďa fultagol, sabu tikkere nden. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaa…ďe nge …ďen lamndoo …ďe : \"E hara jertinoowo araano e mo'on"
  67,9,"∆Āe wi'a: \"Pellet ! Jertinoowo aruno e amen tigi, kono men fenni men wi'i: Allah jippinaali hay e huunde, on wonaali si wanaa e nder majjere mawnde"
  67,10,"∆Āe wi'ita : \"Si me…óen nanaynoo maa hara me…óen haqqilaynoo, men jeyetanooke e yim…ďe Hu…ď…ďunge ngen"
  67,11,∆Āe qirritii junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin. Halakuyee woodanii jom en Hu…ď…ďaynge ngen
  67,12,"Pellet, huloo…ďe Joomi mun …ďen ka wirnii, hino woodani …ďen haforaneede e njo…ďdi mawndi"
  67,13,Suu…óee konngu…ói mon maa …ďanninon …óum. Kanko On ko O anndu…óo ko woni e nder …ďer…óe
  67,14,"E hara tagu…óo On anndaa? Ko Kanko le woni Newii…óo, Humpitii…óo On"
  67,15,"Ko Kanko wa…óani on leydi ndin eltaandi : haray yehee e seraaji mayri, √Īaamon e arsike Makko. Ko ka Makko woni ummital ngal"
  67,16,"E on hooli On won…óo ka kammu nde O munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, Tawa yoo hindi dilla? @Corrected"
  67,17,Kaa on hooli On won…óo ka kammu nde O wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon
  67,18,Sellii adinoo…ďe …ďen …óon …ďen fenniino. Taskii ko honno lette Am …óen wattinirnoo
  67,19,"E …ďee yi'aali colli …óin dow ma…ď…ďe, hi…ói fonta gabitannji …ói √Īobba? [Wonnde] jogitaaki …óin si wanaa Jom hinaraŇčke On. Pellet, ko O reenu…óo kala huunde"
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wanaa Jom hinaraŇčke On? Tigi on, heefer…ďe …ďen wonaali si wanaa e nder hodo"
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si O jogitike arsike Makko on? Si ko woni, …ďe duumike e ∆īaggere e wo…ó…óitagol"
  67,22,Kere ko on yahoowo no hippi yeeso mun …ďuri feewude? Kaa ko on yahoowo no fotondiri e laawol focciingol
  67,23,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni ko fu…ó…ói on, O wa…óani on nan…óe e gii…óe e …ďer…óe\". Kono fan…óii ko yettoton [neema]"
  67,24,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni saakitu…óo on leydi, ko ka Makko kadi woni ko moo…ďitoyte…óon"
  67,25,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on goongu…ďe"
  67,26,"Maaku : \"Anndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Min on ko Mi jertinoowo [tun] …ďanngina"
  67,27,"Nde …ďe yi'oyta (lette) …óen ka …ďadii, geece yeddu…ďe …ďen suni geece heefer…ďe, […ďe] wi'anee : \"Ko …óum …óoo woni ko …óa…ď…ďayno…óon"
  67,28,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si Allah ∆īettitii lam min e wonndii…ďe am maa O yurmaama men, ko hommbo da…óndata heefer…ďe …ďen lette muusu…óe"
  67,29,"Maaku : \"Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŇčke On. Men gom…óinii Mo, ko e Makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde anndon ko hommbo woni e majjere …ďanngunde"
  67,30,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si ndiyam mon …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilay…óam"